{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_08_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 いつか芽吹く日まで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "番組をご覧のみなさん、こんにちは\nアイドルの佐伯遙子、十七歳です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good afternoon‚ everyone watching the program.\nI'm Haruko Saeki‚ an idol‚ seventeen years old.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんは、お肉屋さんのコロッケは好きですか？\n普通のコロッケとひと味違って美味しいですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you all like croquettes from the butcher shop?\nThey're a bit different from regular croquettes and delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0999994278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3666654587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は私の地元、星見市の商店街で\nお肉屋さんのコロッケを食べ比べしてみたいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ in the shopping district of my hometown‚ Hoshimi City‚\nI'd like to try comparing croquettes from the butcher shops.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3666654587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日の仕事は情報番組のレポーターだ。と言っても）\n（馴染みのないケーブルテレビのローカル番組だが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today's job is as a reporter for an informational program. Even so…）\n（It's an unfamiliar local program on cable TV…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7999982834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.0666649501
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "もぐもぐ……うん、美味しい！\nお肉屋さんの揚げたてコロッケは最高ね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Munch munch… Mm‚ great!\nFreshly fried croquettes from the butcher shop are the best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2333316167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9666634242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ローカル番組で食べ比べかぁ……\n人気アイドルへの道は険しいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Comparing croquettes on a local program‚ huh…\nThe road to becoming a popular idol is tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2999947229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.5666613895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "苦労させてしまってすみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for causing you trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5666613895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、お仕事に不満がある訳じゃないのよ\nただ{user}君に申し訳なくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not that I'm unhappy with the job.\nI just feel sorry for you‚ {user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6666613895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5666603723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "人気アイドルの麻奈ちゃんを担当してたから\n私の仕事を見てがっかりしたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since you used to handle the popular idol Mana-chan‚\nyou must be disappointed with my work‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9666603723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "小さな仕事ばかりで\nマネージャーのやりがいがないわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing only small tasks‚ it must feel like\nthere's no challenge as a manager‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9333275476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6333275476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはありません。今は小さな案件ばかりでも\n遙子さんなら必ず大きな仕事がくるようになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. Even if it's only small jobs for now‚\nwith you‚ Haruko-san‚ bigger opportunities will surely come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5999942142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0666603723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえるのは嬉しいけど\n麻奈ちゃんに比べて私は地味だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nice to hear you say that‚ but…\nCompared to Mana-chan‚ I'm plain and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2999937056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "魅力は人それぞれです\n遙子さんには麻奈にはない魅力があるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has their own charm.\nHaruko-san‚ you have a charm that Mana doesn't‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7333300907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.0333295821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんにはない、私の魅力……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A charm that Mana-chan doesn't have…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0333295821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3333280562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "辛い時でも笑顔を絶やさず、気遣いを忘れない……\n遙子さんには人を安心させる癒やしの空気があります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even in tough times‚ you always smile and never forget to be considerate…\nHaruko-san‚ you have a comforting presence that puts people at ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1666613895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "それは、私に出来ることをやってるだけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just doing what I can…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3666608809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.4666603723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだとしても、遙子さんのように\n自然に出来る人はなかなかいないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ not everyone can\nnaturally do what Haruko-san do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0999937056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私には麻奈ちゃんのような\n歌やダンスの才能はないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't have the talent for singing and\ndancing like Mana-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3333270389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.2333270389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは地道に努力して、着実に力を付けています\n積み重ねた努力は絶対に無駄にはなりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ you're steadily gaining strength through your efforts.\nThe effort you've put in won't go to waste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1333270389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんも麻奈と同じように、あの三枝さんが見出して\nスカウトしたんですから、もっと自信持って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like Mana‚ Saegusa-san discovered and\nscouted you. Have more confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1666654585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.199979464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}君は\n私が売れるって本当に信じてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Do {user} really believe that\nI'll become famous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0333127973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.2333127973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前じゃないですか\n俺は遙子さんのマネージャーなんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI'm your manager‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3333127973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "一週間だけ、だけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just for a week‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2666430788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.1666369754
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。麻奈ちゃんのようにはなれなくても\n私らしいやり方でトップアイドルになる道があるわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. Even if I can't be like Mana-chan‚\nthere's a way for me to become a top idol in my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7333036421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
