    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君のマネージャー期間も\n今日で終わり……一週間、あっという間だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ your time as my manager\nends today… It flew by in just a week‚ didn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.199950981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "結局、あまり役に立てなくてすみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry I wasn't very helpful after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.6332904178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないわよ\n君がいてくれて、とっても心強かったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true at all.\nYour presence was very reassuring for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.8666166304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで{user}君や星見プロへの\n感謝の気持ちを再認識出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ I was able to reaffirm my gratitude\nto you and Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.1666166304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "……実はね、麻奈ちゃんと\nいつか二人で一緒にライブをやろうねって話してたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Actually‚ Mana-chan and I\nwere talking about doing a live together someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.3332812625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　どうしたんですか\n急に話題が変わりましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What's going on?\nYou suddenly changed the topic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.5999479292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……突然ライブの話なんて意味が分からないわよね\nでも、そのままでいいから聞いてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chuckles… I guess talking about a live out of the blue is strange‚ isn't it?\nBut can you hear me out anyway?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.1332894006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "まだ日程は決まってないけど、時間が掛かっても\n絶対にやりたいって、改めて強く思ったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The date isn't set yet‚ but even if it takes time‚\nI strongly want to do it‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.6332894006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "二人でライブをやる時は、{user}君も\n観に来てくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Mana-chan and I do a live together‚\nwill you come to watch‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.8332894006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\n麻奈と遙子さんが一緒に歌うなんて見逃せませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI can't miss seeing Mana and Haruko-san sing together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.9666298547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり期待はしないでね。私は麻奈ちゃんほど\n歌も踊りも上手じゃないし、華もないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't expect too much. I'm not as good at singing or\ndancing as Mana‚ and I'm not as gorgeous…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.1332965213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは自分で思っているより\nずっと素晴らしいアイドルですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san is a much more wonderful idol\nthan you give yourself credit for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.79995505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "だから失敗を恐れないで\nやりたいと思ったことは思い切って挑戦して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don't be afraid of failure.\nGo ahead and challenge what you want to do with all your heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.6999733605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\nいつか私にチャンスが巡ってきたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nSomeday‚ if a chance comes my way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.7666522341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "今の{user}君の言葉を思い出して\n失敗を恐れずに、思い切って挑戦してみるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll remember your words‚ {user}‚\nand I'll try to challenge without fear of failure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.9999631879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈ちゃんとのライブ\nちゃんと出来るか不安だったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was anxious about whether I could do a live with Mana‚\nbut talking with you‚ {user}‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.1999733604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk029.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君と話してたら、不安よりも\n楽しみな気持ちが大きくなってきちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm feeling more excited than anxious now.\nI'm also looking forward to the day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.1999489463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "俺も、麻奈と遙子さんが\n一緒のステージに立つ日を楽しみにしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also look forward to watching\nMana and Haruko-san stand on the same stage together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.2665993369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_02-hrk030.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに待たせないと思うから、楽しみに待っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think you'll have to wait too long‚ so look forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.8332660035,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}